Boko Haram Extends Its Grip in Nigeria
Boko Haram’s weekend seizure of a Nigerian army outpost that was to serve as a command center for combating the Islamist insurgency offers another measure of how fast the country’s military is losing ground and how multinational efforts have stalled. (Further reading:Satellite Images ‘Show Boko Haram Massacre’ in Nigeria).
